&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0.0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1202&quot; data-local-id=&quot;e7cdaf6cb980&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Are you passionate about building production-ready AI systems? Join our Setup &amp;amp; Rollout team, the team behind Dashlane&#39;s AI Advisor, where you&#39;ll help build confidential AI experiences that millions of users can trust.&lt;/p&gt;
