&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0.0in;&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for people who actively use AI tools to drive efficiency, creativity, and impact in their work. At Dashlane, we drive innovation and value learning, strive for excellence in everything we do, and thrive as one team. Learn more about&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://lifeatdashlane.com/&quot; data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;mark&quot; data-prosemirror-mark-name=&quot;link&quot;&gt;&lt;u data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;mark&quot; data-prosemirror-mark-name=&quot;underline&quot;&gt;life at Dashlane&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, including &lt;a href=&quot;https://lifeatdashlane.com/how-we-work&quot; data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;mark&quot; data-prosemirror-mark-name=&quot;link&quot;&gt;&lt;u data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;mark&quot; data-prosemirror-mark-name=&quot;underline&quot;&gt;how we work&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://lifeatdashlane.com/how-we-hire&quot; data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;mark&quot; data-prosemirror-mark-name=&quot;link&quot;&gt;&lt;u data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;mark&quot; data-prosemirror-mark-name=&quot;underline&quot;&gt;how we hire&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, and the &lt;a href=&quot;https://lifeatdashlane.com/benefits-dashlane&quot; data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;mark&quot; data-prosemirror-mark-name=&quot;link&quot;&gt;&lt;u data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;mark&quot; data-prosemirror-mark-name=&quot;underline&quot;&gt;benefits of being a Dashlaner&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0.0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;808&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;fabric-text-color-mark&quot; data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot; data-text-custom-color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;About the role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1218&quot; data-local-id=&quot;5a0c3e7b319f&quot;&gt;As a Server Software Engineer, you will own the design and implementation of core backend solutions that directly impact our business growth and partner onboarding ecosystems. You will work in a highly collaborative environment alongside Senior and Staff engineers who provide continuous mentorship, while partnering closely with product managers, project managers, and quality engineering teams. The Setup &amp;amp; Rollout team is currently focused on optimizing administrative workflows and scaling system integrations to ensure smooth deployments. Over your first 12 months, you will build full autonomy across all features and codebase areas you contribute to.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1877&quot; data-local-id=&quot;ac41ff88e19c&quot;&gt;In this role, you will combine strong backend expertise with a forward-thinking AI mindset, integrating GenAI tools throughout the &lt;span data-highlighted=&quot;true&quot; data-vc=&quot;highlighted-text&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;_kqswh2mm&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;_5pioz8co _189e1dm9 _1il9buyh _19lc184f _d0altlke&quot; data-testid=&quot;definition-highlighter&quot;&gt;SDLC&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; to accelerate development velocity while working in a deeply collaborative team to secure millions of digital identities.&lt;/p&gt;
